name: OpenBuild
fullText:
🎉 Starknet Build Station 圆满收官！

💻 为期5天的线下加速节点，脑洞狂飙、灵感爆炸，来自各地的 builder 聚在一起，边敲代码边聊理想，完全停不下来！

💗 感谢 @StarknetFndn 联合 @OpenBuildxyz 和 @coset_io 安排了这场开发狂欢！🚀 属于 builder 的夏天刚刚开始！

💪 期待更多 builders https://t.co/XForcCuEbT

name: Colosseum
fullText:
The @Solana Breakout Hackathon has concluded. Thanks to all of the builders who entered products!

We're organizing the submissions & preparing to initiate the judging process, which will take 4 weeks.

We will announce the total # of submissions & share a public directory soon. https://t.co/X7MAOl04j5
